wiki.summary: "Dash" is a song by South Korean girl group Nmixx for their second extended play Fe3O4: Break. It was released as the EP's lead single by JYP Entertainment and Republic Records on January 15, 2024. On November 28, 2023, JYP Entertainment announced Nmixx would be releasing their second EP titled Fe3O4: Break on January 15, 2024. On January 6, 2024, "Dash" was announced as the lead track of the album with the release of the track listing, followed by the release of a teaser for its music video on January 13. Read more on Last.fm.
